    <step order="1" name="Add hook Step">After worktree scaffolded: if matching Project Issue exists (search by branch name), call `/devops-project-register` to link. Else prompt for registration.</step>
    <step order="2" name="Smoke test">Both happy paths: linked + prompted.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
